---
title: Double Smokey Chicken Drumsticks & Roast Veggies with Truffle Mayonnaise & Roasted Almonds
description: Tried and true chicken and veg just had a major makeover! This chicken is marinated in Aussie spice blend and honey for a sweet and smokey hit and is accompanied by a rainbow of roasted veggies. A dollop of creamy Italian truffle mayo is the perfect  addition to tie it all together.
